page.title: 17A TYPICAL HOUSE IN COLEHILL.
page.content: I live at 124 Bridleway, Bridleway Park Colehill, Wimborne, Dorset. My house is new and it is made from bricks and the top is painted. It is a detached house with quite a big garden at the back and front. In the back garden there is no grass, just mud, but in the front garden there is grass. In the back garden there are four evergreen trees and in the front there are three trees, but we do not know what they are. Inside my house we have got a kitchen with fitted cupboards and an oven. We have got a lounge with a dining room at the end with a serving hatch . We have got a downstairs bedroom-study. Upstairs we have three bedrooms, one bathroom and three toilets. In the front garden we have a garage and we have one yellow car. {VANESSA REW. AGED 9 YEARS.
